query:
Compute the limit $\displaystyle \lim_{n\to \infty}\dfrac{y_n}{x_n}$, where the two sequence $\{x_n\}, \{y_n\}$ are defined by 
\[ \left(
    \begin{array}{c}
      x_n \\
      y_n \\
    \end{array}
  \right)=A^n\left(
    \begin{array}{c}
      1 \\
      1 \\
    \end{array}
  \right)
\] with  $A=\left(
                  \begin{array}{cc}
                    0 & 1 \\
                    1 & 1 \\
                  \end{array}
                \right)
$.

